        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Currently {{getMessages()}} returns error messages for input values that are present, and failed validation.\n{{getMissing()}} returns error messages for input values that are required, but missing.\n\nThis is a request to make getMessages() return the {{array_merge()}} of messages for both failed and missing fields.\n\nThe separate groups of error messages should be retrieved by {{getMissing()}} and {{getInvalid()}}.  (see ZF-1450)."
